<article id="post-5" class="post-5 page type-page status-publish hentry">
	<header class="entry-header">
		<h1 class="entry-title">British Columbia Aboriginal Network on Disability Society (BCANDS)</h1>
	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	<div class="entry-content">
		<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #800000;"><em><strong>* If you are experiencing difficulties viewing our site, pages and links, please ensure that your browser has been updated! Best viewed using Mozilla Firefox.<br />
</strong></em></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><em><span style="color: #800000;"><strong>* For the text to voice option, on any page of the BCANDS website, simply highlight the text you wish to hear and click on the speaker icon!</strong></span></em></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">______________________________________________________________________</p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a href="http://www.bcands.bc.ca/wp-content/uploads/JGF-Award.jpg" target="_blank"><img class="alignnone wp-image-3247" src="http://www.bcands.bc.ca/wp-content/uploads/JGF-Award-300x300.jpg" alt="JGF Award" width="50" height="50" srcset="http://www.bcands.bc.ca/wp-content/uploads/JGF-Award-300x300.jpg 300w, http://www.bcands.bc.ca/wp-content/uploads/JGF-Award-150x150.jpg 150w, http://www.bcands.bc.ca/wp-content/uploads/JGF-Award-1024x1022.jpg 1024w, http://www.bcands.bc.ca/wp-content/uploads/JGF-Award-301x300.jpg 301w" sizes="(max-width: 50px) 100vw, 50px" /></a>  <a href="http://www.bcands.bc.ca/wp-content/uploads/Best-Practices-2014-2015.jpg"><img class="alignnone wp-image-2325" src="http://www.bcands.bc.ca/wp-content/uploads/Best-Practices-2014-2015-300x236.jpg" alt="Best Practices 2014 - 2015" width="55" height="45" /></a>  <a href="http://www.bcands.bc.ca/wp-content/uploads/2014-Deryck-Thomson-Award.jpg"><img class="alignnone wp-image-2085" src="http://www.bcands.bc.ca/wp-content/uploads/2014-Deryck-Thomson-Award-300x240.jpg" alt="2014 Deryck Thomson Award" width="56" height="46" srcset="http://www.bcands.bc.ca/wp-content/uploads/2014-Deryck-Thomson-Award-300x240.jpg 300w, http://www.bcands.bc.ca/wp-content/uploads/2014-Deryck-Thomson-Award-1024x820.jpg 1024w, http://www.bcands.bc.ca/wp-content/uploads/2014-Deryck-Thomson-Award-374x300.jpg 374w" sizes="(max-width: 56px) 100vw, 56px" /></a>  <a href="http://www.bcands.bc.ca/wp-content/uploads/2013-Dr.-Nancy-Hall-Award.jpg"><img class=" wp-image-2084 alignnone" src="http://www.bcands.bc.ca/wp-content/uploads/2013-Dr.-Nancy-Hall-Award-300x201.jpg" alt="2013 Dr. Nancy Hall Award" width="65" height="48" /></a>   <a href="http://www.bcands.bc.ca/wp-content/uploads/2013-BCMA-Award.jpg"><img class="alignnone wp-image-2083" src="http://www.bcands.bc.ca/wp-content/uploads/2013-BCMA-Award-300x211.jpg" alt="2013 BCMA Award" width="63" height="47" /></a>  <a href="http://www.bcands.bc.ca/wp-cont